data.description: Welcome to your new home in the prestigious master-planned golf course community of Windrose! This stunning property boasts four spacious bedrooms and 3 1/2 baths, including a luxurious primary suite. The home also features a versatile game room and a convenient home office, perfect for remote work or study.  As you step into the home, you'll be greeted by a soaring two-story entry and family room, flooded with an abundance of natural light flanked by dual staricases with an open floor plan and Island Kitchen. The neutral color palette throughout creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, allowing you to easily personalize the space to your liking. Updated Jack and Jill bathroom shower that offers a modern and sleek design. Enjoy all the amazing amenities this neighborhood has to offer, including two refreshing pools, a kiddie pool and a serene natural lake with shaded paved walking paths, tennis + sports fields & easy access to the nearby dining,retail, Klein Schools and Grand Parkway!
